reviewText:
Great experience.  I would use again.

@

Great information! I highly recommend the video. However, I purchased what I thought were discs 1&2 in the ground fighting series. One was labeled 1. Defending From the Ground. The other was labeled 2. Attacking From the Ground. To my consternation they are both the same material! And I didn't open the second disc before it was too late to return it. This may have been a labeling error. You may want to contact the seller before purchasing to ensure that there really are two separate discs.
Liked some concepts but some others I feel will get a civilian thrown in jail.
It is not Krav Maga  as such but techniques are similar
